Micro services overview

Services                    Description                      Example endpoint

Auth-services             handles user registration and login   /register ,/login 

product-services         manages product catalog                /product ,/product/<id>

order-services          Handles order place ment and            /order,/order/<id>
                        retrieval 

_____--------------------------------------___________________________________________-----------------------___________

How it works :

1. User signs up / login -> auth-services  validates and issues a token
2. User browses produckts -> Product -services fetches list
3. User places order -> order-service stores order details and confirms

Each service exposes Rest api and the frontend (optional) can call then independently 


